<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>Confirm Your Presave</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 30px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 10px 10px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background: #ffffff;
            padding: 30px;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
        }
        .song-info {
            background: #f5f5f5;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .song-title {
            font-size: 20px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #333;
            margin: 0 0 10px 0;
        }
        .artist-name {
            font-size: 16px;
            color: #666;
            margin: 0;
        }
        .confirm-button {
            display: inline-block;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
            color: white;
            padding: 15px 40px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: bold;
            font-size: 16px;
            margin: 20px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .button-container {
            text-align: center;
            margin: 30px 0;
        }
        .footer {
            background: #f9f9f9;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 0 0 10px 10px;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
            border-top: none;
        }
        .note {
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #666;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>ðŸŽµ Confirm Your Presave</h1>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
        
        <p>Thank you for signing up to presave this amazing release!</p>
        
        <div class="song-info">
            <p class="song-title">"{{songTitle}}"</p>
            <p class="artist-name">by {{artistName}}</p>
        </div>
        
        <p>We're excited to have you on board! Please click the button below to confirm your email address and complete your presave signup:</p>
        
        <div class="button-container">
            <a href="{{confirmationLink}}" class="confirm-button">Confirm Presave</a>
        </div>
        
        <p class="note">
            <strong>What happens next?</strong><br>
            Once you confirm, we'll send you a reminder email on release day with a direct link to listen on your preferred streaming platform!
        </p>
        
        <p class="note">
            If you didn't sign up for this presave, please ignore this email.
        </p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="footer">
        <p>
            Thank you for supporting independent music!<br>
            <strong>- The RatedaFRiKa Team</strong>
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 12px; color: #999; margin-top: 10px;">
            This email was sent because you signed up for a presave on RatedaFRiKa.
        </p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>

